outgoingDisclaimer: Jakákoli zpráva, kterou sem pošleš, bude odeslána adminům.
dmError: Omlouváme se, ale tento příkaz nelze provést v soukromých zprávách.
noContext: You haven't provided the context! Please add both the string ID and the context explaining it.
noQuote: You haven't provided a quote! In order to request one to be added, execute `+quote add <quote> / <author mention>`.
noUserQuote: Nezadal jsi jméno uživatele! Prosím napiš citát a následně označ citovaného uživatele, odděleného lomítkem.
noPlayer: That player has never joined Hypixel!
noTrPr: Nejsi překladatel ani korektor, takže to nemůžeš použít!
noPermission: You're not allowed to execute this command on this channel!
contextSubArg:
Please enter a subcommand as first argument. This can either be `get`, `add`, `edit`, `link` or `help`.
For information, run `+context help`.
apiError: Something went wrong while contacting the API!
secondLeft: Please wait another second to use `+%%command%%` again.
timeLeftT: Počkej prosím dalších %%time%% sekund/y pro použití příkazu `+%%command%%`.
minsLeftT: Počkej prosím ještě %%time%% minut/y, abys mohl znovu použít `+%%command%%`.
linkCorrectionDesc: Please change your link to the %%format%% format next time.

tips.translators: I need translators! Find out how to become a bot translator at %%translate%%.
tips.prefix: Do you wanna have a cool prefix on your nickname? Run `+prefix` in %%bots%% and follow the instructions! Available to all Hypixel and Quickplay translators.
tips.enen: Prosím, změň své odkazy na en-en!
tips.xp: You get random amounts of XP every minute when you're chatting, which will eventually make you level up.
tips.moreTips: Potřebujeme více tipů! Navrhni je pomocí `+feedback`.
tips.guide: Did you know we have a guide on how to get started with Crowdin, available for all translators? Check it out at %%gettingStarted%%, it has some useful tips!
tips.twitter: Have you followed our twitter account? Check it out at %%twitter%%!
tips.rulesInfo: %%rules%% and %%serverInfo%% have all the info you need about this server!
tips.fixTranslation: Found a mistake in a translation? Contact a proofreader for your language or let people know in a translation channel.
tips.pinnedInfo: Did you know most channels have important information pinned? You should check it out every time you visit one!
tips.hypixelStats: You can view information about a specific player on Hypixel by executing `+hypixelstats <username>`!
